	* libtomboy/eggtrayicon.c: Patch from Dan Winship to setup tray
	icon transparency.

	A few more tomboy-0-4 merges...
	
	* Tomboy/NoteTag.cs: XX_Large -> XXLarge.

	* Tomboy/Watchers.cs: SetText -> Text.

